Package: reading-guide
Version: 1.1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6, libgtk-3-0 (>= 3.22), libx11-6, libxext6
Maintainer: Anna <a.tishelman.inbox@gmail.com>
Description: High-performance horizontal reading guide for deep focus.
 This utility provides a customizable, non-interactive overlay strip that 
 tracks the mouse cursor tip with mathematical precision. 
 .
 Features include:
  * Persistent settings: Automatically saves and restores configuration from ~/.reading_guide_config.
  * Multi-threaded stability: Independent X11 display connections to prevent UI freezing.
  * Visual focus modes: Adjustable masking (above, below, or full) and smooth shadow rendering.
  * Surgical UI: Clear, labeled control panel for thickness, color, and opacity.
